  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595974412832-BH9COBLC2XY314SR0B11/2a-Rainbow%2Bscripted%2Bquote%2Bby%2BAmy%2BTangerine.png\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Scripted this for Motivational Monday and shared it only on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BCYD8mhtnjX/\">Instagram</a>. (Sorry for the delay here!) If you've been following along there, you'll know that I spent the leap year day - February 29 - at Facebook and Instagram Headquarters! Hoping to share more about that soon. Also, I'm currently in Toronto, so there's a lot of travel vlogs and creative stuff that's happening.</p><p>I also took video while scripting the quote, which <a href=\"https://youtu.be/hNc01WJLINw\">you can see on YouTube</a>. </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
